<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to 9ja Market</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #009933;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      h1,
      h2 {
        color: #009933;
      }
      .steps {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .steps li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #009933;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
      .categories {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .category {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 5px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        width: calc(50% - 20px);
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to 9ja Market!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</h2>

      <p>
        Thank you for joining 9ja Market! We're excited to have you as part of
        our community. Now you can easily discover and purchase products from
        local merchants across Nigeria.
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Your account is now active and ready to use!</strong>
      </div>

      <h3>Here's how to get started:</h3>

      <ol class="steps">
        <li>
          <strong>Browse Products</strong> - Search for any product you desire
          across numerous markets and merchants.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Connect with Merchants</strong> - Contact merchants directly
          or purchase products through our secure platform.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Secure Checkout</strong> - Use our safe transaction system to
          pay for your products with confidence.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Track Orders</strong> - Follow your purchases from order
          confirmation to delivery.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3>Explore Popular Product Categories:</h3>

      <div class="categories">
        <div class="category">Food & Groceries</div>
        <div class="category">Fashion & Accessories</div>
        <div class="category">Electronics & Gadgets</div>
        <div class="category">Home & Living</div>
        <div class="category">Health & Wellness</div>
        <div class="category">Traditional Crafts</div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight">
        <p>
          <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Save your favorite merchants to quickly find
          them again during future shopping trips!
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Our platform connects you with authentic products from verified
        merchants throughout Nigeria. If you find something you like, you can
        easily contact the merchant, make a purchase, and arrange for delivery.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, our customer support team
        is ready to help you.
      </p>

      <p>
        Happy shopping!<br />
        The 9ja Market Team
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 9ja Market - Connecting Local Markets Across Nigeria</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
